TESTIMONIALS

“ Assalamalaikum warahmatullahi wabarakatuhu, Prophet Muhammad (blessings and peace of Allah be upon him) said:

“Allah, the angels, the inhabitants of heaven and earth, even the ant in its hole and even the fish in the sea, send blessings upon the one who teaches the people good.”

 

Allah (swt), the omnipotent, the most gracious and the most merciful, has lead me from darkness to light with my enrolment into the prodigious institute , AlKalaam Institute, Mysore.
Alhamdullilah, it has been a transformational experience over the past 5 years. AlKalaam Institute indeed has scaled great feats in educating and illuminating the soul of many.

 

I’m grateful to Allah (swt) and indebted to this institution in guiding me and succouring me in this beautiful journey towards Islam. May Allah (swt) grant hidayat, righteousness and blessings to this institution Ameen. Jazakallahu khairan.”

— Lamees HS, Batch of 2016
